  "page": "Game of Thrones: Ascent",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center;\"><i>Game of Thrones: Ascent</i></th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Developer(s)</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disruptor_Beam\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Disruptor Beam\">Disruptor Beam</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Platform(s)</th><td>\niPad, Facebook, and Kongregate</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Release date(s)</th><td>\n2013</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\nEnglish</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre(s)</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/social_network_game\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:social network game\">social media</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Players</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Massively_multiplayer_online_role-playing_game\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Massively multiplayer online role-playing game\">MMORPG</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Game of Thrones: Ascent</b></i> is a free-to-play <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/social_network_game\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:social network game\">social media</a> game developed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disruptor_Beam\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Disruptor Beam\">Disruptor Beam</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SG_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SG-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> First released as an open beta on Facebook in February 2013,<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Massively_multiplayer_online_role-playing_game\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Massively multiplayer online role-playing game\">MMORPG</a> is now available for iPad, Facebook, and Kongregate.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> An Android tablet version is planned for future release.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>, the \"designers took great pains to make sure the flavor of <a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">the novels</a> is here. [He] saw alliance building, treachery, marriages, murders, and most of all the constant struggle to be the greatest house in Westeros.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-SG_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SG-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Disruptor Beam shut down the game on January 3, 2019.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Game_of_Thrones:_Ascent&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-SG-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-SG_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-SG_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Not A Blog: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://grrm.livejournal.com/280977.html\">Social Gaming</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Kotaku: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kotaku.com/5986013/facebook-is-the-perfect-place-to-play-a-game-of-thrones\">Facebook is the Perfect Place to Play a Game of Thrones</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Kotaku: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kotaku.com/game-of-thrones-ascent-is-more-up-to-date-with-the-sho-476864152\"><i>Game of Thrones: Ascent</i> is More Up-to-Date With the Show Than You Are</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Not A Blog: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://grrm.livejournal.com/362212.html\">Game of Thrones: Ascent for iPad </a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gotascent.fandom.com/wiki/Main_Page\">Game of Thrones: Ascent Wiki</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Game_of_Thrones:_Ascent&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.disruptorbeam.com/games/game-of-thrones\">Disruptor Beam</a> (no longer active)</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Game_of_Thrones_Ascent\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Game of Thrones Ascent\">Wikipedia: Game of Thrones Ascent</a></li></ul>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\